long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Blast off into the galaxy and embark on thrilling space adventures in Starship! Take command of your own starship, explore distant planets, and engage in epic battles against alien fleets. Upgrade your ship with powerful weapons, shields, and engines to overcome enemies and survive the dangers of deep space. Navigate through asteroid fields, discover hidden treasures, and complete daring missions to unlock new galaxies. With stunning visuals and fast-paced action, Starship offers an immersive experience that lets you become the ultimate space captain. Are you ready to conquer the stars?
